### How to update

- To update this addon simply remove your existing ps2-drops folder and upload the new one.
- Afterwards please change the map. If changes don't apply, please restart your server.
- Configuration and created items will stay the same when updating.

**Important**: When you upload files don't forget to check for failed transfers. (Tab at the bottom if using FileZilla)


